summary: The most beautiful high elf in Skyrim - at least in your game if you use her :)
descriptionHtml:
Since I played a high elf mage in Oblivion (http://www.tesnexus.com/downloads/file.php?id=5398), I wanted to do so again in Skyrim.

So, continuing from last time, here is my Skyrim high elf.

As you know, the default Skyrim high elves are ugly and if you\'ve tried you\'ll know that getting them to look decent is very very hard. A lot harder than in Oblivion.
author: chanon
